          {
            "name": "idle_times",
            "type": 2,
            "code": "assign 0"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "file": "mtn/Live2D_peridod012.mtn",
        "text": "戦場に彷徨う魂狩り放題、といったものはないのか？不公平じゃのう。",
        "sound": "sound/120.wav",
        "var_floats": [
          {
            "name": "idle_times",
            "type": 1,
            "code": "lower $max_idle_times"
          },
          {
            "name": "idle_times",
            "type": 2,
            "code": "assign 0"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "file": "mtn/Live2D_peridod013.mtn",
        "text": "この格好が原因ということはわかっておるが…ええい！うざったい視線じゃな！そんなに見るでない！",
        "sound": "sound/130.wav",
        "var_floats": [
          {
            "name": "idle_times",
            "type": 1,
            "code": "lower $max_idle_times"
          },
          {
            "name": "idle_times",
            "type": 2,
            "code": "assign 0"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "file": "mtn/Live2D_peridod014.mtn",
        "text": "どうにも腹が減った…アーサー…お主の魂、うまそうじゃのう…心配するな、優しくしてやるからの…",
        "sound": "sound/140.wav",
        "var_floats": [
          {
            "name": "idle_times",
            "type": 1,
            "code": "lower $max_idle_times"
          },
          {
            "name": "idle_times",
            "type": 2,
            "code": "assign 0"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "file": "mtn/Live2D_peridod015.mtn",
        "text": "んん…「さんおいる」とは中々気持ちの良いものじゃな。もっと頼めるかの？アーサー。",
        "sound": "sound/150.wav",
        "var_floats": [
          {
            "name": "idle_times",
            "type": 1,
            "code": "lower $max_idle_times"
          },
          {
            "name": "idle_times",
            "type": 2,
            "code": "assign 0"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "file": "mtn/Live2D_peridod016.mtn",
        "text": "ふぅむ…アーサー…それ以上触るのであれば、覚悟はできているのであろうな？",
        "sound": "sound/160.wav",
        "var_floats": [
          {
            "name": "idle_times",
            "type": 1,
            "code": "lower $max_idle_times"
          },
          {
            "name": "idle_times",
            "type": 2,
            "code": "assign 0"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "file": "mtn/Live2D_peridod017.mtn",
        "text": "特別にわらわの頭を撫でることを許そう。他の者にはほいほいするでないぞ？",
        "sound": "sound/170.wav",
        "var_floats": [
          {
            "name": "idle_times",
            "type": 1,
            "code": "lower $max_idle_times"
          },
          {
            "name": "idle_times",
            "type": 2,
            "code": "assign 0"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "file": "mtn/Live2D_peridod018.mtn",
        "text": "ふっ。この程度で頬を赤らめるほど初心ではないわ。人生経験の差、といったところかの。",
        "sound": "sound/180.wav",
        "var_floats": [
          {
            "name": "idle_times",
            "type": 1,
            "code": "lower $max_idle_times"
          },
          {
            "name": "idle_times",
            "type": 2,
            "code": "assign 0"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "file": "mtn/Live2D_peridod019.mtn",
        "text": "なんじゃさっきからじろじろと。ようやくわらわに惚れたか？",
        "sound": "sound/190.wav",
        "var_floats": [
          {
            "name": "idle_times",
            "type": 1,
            "code": "lower $max_idle_times"
          },
          {
            "name": "idle_times",
            "type": 2,
            "code": "assign 0"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "file": "mtn/Live2D_peridod020.mtn",
        "text": "わらわの身体に興味があるか。よいじゃろう。もっと近くに来い。",
        "sound": "sound/200.wav",
        "var_floats": [
          {
            "name": "idle_times",
            "type": 1,
            "code": "lower $max_idle_times"
          },
          {
            "name": "idle_times",
            "type": 2,
            "code": "assign 0"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "file": "mtn/Live2D_peridod001.mtn",
        "text": "ここでお主を待たなければならぬとは……サポート、というのは存外つまらんのう。",
        "sound": "sound/010.wav",
        "var_floats": [
          {
            "name": "idle_times",
            "type": 1,
            "code": "greater_equal $max_idle_times"
          },
          {
            "name": "idle_times",
            "type": 2,
            "code": "assign 0"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "file": "mtn/Live2D_peridod002.mtn",
        "text": "傭兵を見てるとついからかってみたくなってしまうのじゃ。狼狽えている姿が中々可愛くてのう。",
        "sound": "sound/020.wav",
        "var_floats": [
          {
            "name": "idle_times",
            "type": 1,
            "code": "greater_equal $max_idle_times"
          },
          {
            "name": "idle_times",
            "type": 2,
            "code": "assign 0"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "file": "mtn/Live2D_peridod003.mtn",
        "text": "富豪は「交易」というものを目指しているのだったなあやつの魂は色々なものを吸収している気がするのう",
        "sound": "sound/030.wav",
        "var_floats": [
          {
            "name": "idle_times",
            "type": 1,
            "code": "greater_equal $max_idle_times"
          },
          {
            "name": "idle_times",
            "type": 2,
            "code": "assign 0"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "file": "mtn/Live2D_peridod004.mtn",
        "text": "盗賊のやつ、わらわの胸ばかりじろじろ見おって…。男共より鬼気迫る表情じゃったぞ…。",
        "sound": "sound/040.wav",
        "var_floats": [
          {
            "name": "idle_times",
            "type": 1,
            "code": "greater_equal $max_idle_times"
          },
          {
            "name": "idle_times",
            "type": 2,
            "code": "assign 0"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "file": "mtn/Live2D_peridod005.mtn",
        "text": "歌姫は良い声をしておるのう。魂狩りの時の断末魔もさぞかし美しいのじゃろうなあ…。じゅる…。",
        "sound": "sound/050.wav",
        "var_floats": [
          {
            "name": "idle_times",
            "type": 1,
            "code": "greater_equal $max_idle_times"
          },
          {
            "name": "idle_times",
            "type": 2,
            "code": "assign 0"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "file": "mtn/Live2D_peridod006.mtn",
        "text": "暇じゃ、アーサー。それに腹が減った。街に繰り出して子供の魂でも狩りに行かんか？…冗談じゃ。",
        "sound": "sound/060.wav",
        "var_floats": [
          {
            "name": "idle_times",
            "type": 1,
            "code": "greater_equal $max_idle_times"
          },
          {
            "name": "idle_times",
            "type": 2,
            "code": "assign 0"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "file": "mtn/Live2D_peridod007.mtn",
        "text": "あついぞアーサー！なーんもやる気がせん。死神もバテバテじゃし…わらわもアイスが食べたいのう。",
        "sound": "sound/070.wav",
        "var_floats": [
          {
            "name": "idle_times",
            "type": 1,
            "code": "greater_equal $max_idle_times"
          },
          {
